---

### [choco://intel-proset-drivers](choco://intel-proset-drivers/s=https://nuts.bcurran3.org/nuget/chocolatey/)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [choco:// Protocol support ](https://nuts.bcurran3.org/feeds/chocolatey/choco-protocol-support/versions)


---

The xx.xxx.x package installs the Windows® 10 and Windows 11* Wi-Fi drivers for Intel® Wireless Adapters.

See the release notes for what's new or fixed, known issues, and supported hardware.



